^m(\\mathcal{X}),$ then \\begin{align} \\text{(p-adic Functional\nWelch Bounds)} \\quad \\max_{1\\leq j,k \\leq n, j \\neq k}\\{|n|,\n|f_j(\\tau_k)f_k(\\tau_j)|^{m} \\}\\geq \\frac{|n|^2}{\\left|{d+m-1 \\choose m}\\right|\n}. \\end{align} We formulate non-Archimedean functional and p-adic functional\nZauner conjectures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2022 09:11:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-15"}
